Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.60,0:49:14.95,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,proudícímu z melodie houslí.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.95,0:49:19.10,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,Násherně si zatančeme!
